WEBVTT

00:14:59.714 --> 00:15:01.651
your friends and family.

00:15:01.651 --> 00:15:05.097
Recast survivors as wonderful, lovable people

00:15:05.097 --> 00:15:07.912
with full futures.

00:15:07.912 --> 00:15:11.393
Recognize the early signs of violence

00:15:11.393 --> 00:15:14.226
and conscientiously intervene,

00:15:14.226 --> 00:15:18.388
deescalate it, show victims a safe way out.

00:15:18.388 --> 00:15:22.383
Together we can make our beds,

00:15:22.383 --> 00:15:26.000
our dinner tables and our families

00:15:26.000 --> 00:15:29.257
the safe and peaceful oases they should be.

00:15:29.257 --> 00:15:31.229
Thank you.